Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.66,0:42:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnCalibri\fs25\b1}Je v poriadku sa do niekoho zamilovať?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.64,0:42:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnCalibri\fs25\b1}Aj keď pri tom zraníte niekoho iného?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.97,0:42:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnCalibri\fs25\b1}Keby som sa reinkarnoval...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.96,0:42:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnCalibri\fs25\b1}Chcel by som byť znova s tebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.96,0:42:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnCalibri\fs25\b1}Asa-chan!\NAsa-chan! Asa-chan!
